## EzProduct
```python
from ezweb import EzProduct

url = "https://www.razer.com/gaming-laptops/Razer-Blade-15/RZ09-0409JED3-R3U1"

page = EzProduct(url)

print(page.json_summary)
```
Output:
```json
{
    "provider": {
        "name": "Razer",
        "domain": "razer.com",
        "addresses": null,
        "phone": []
    },
